videos.description: Illinois' Kofi Cockburn dominates the first half in scoring with 16 points, including a powerful slam, to put the Fighting Illini up 40-29 at halftime.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Highlight (Cockburn drops 16 in the 1st half on Minnesota) 2020/12/15 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Cockburn drops 16 in the 1st half on Minnesota

videos.description: Kofi Cockburn rocks the rim with a powerful, one-handed slam with a slew of Minnesota defenders on his case.
videos.headline: Cockburn stuffs it home

videos.description: Kofi Cockburn records a double-double to help No. 13 Illinois cruise to a 92-65 win over Minnesota.

videos.headline: Cockburn's 33 points, 13 boards lead Illinois to easy victory

videos.description: Andre Curbelo fights to hold on to the ball and pulls up for a 3-pointer just as time expires on the shot clock.
